        <widget class="QLabel" name="label_2">
         <property name="text">
          <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;Soon, a brand new method of mining will be added to Litecoin Cash.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Hive, our agent-based mining proposal, is centered around the concept of &lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;worker bees&lt;/span&gt;. These worker bees can be created by any LCC holder, who then becomes a &lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;beekeeper&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Once mature, worker bees have a finite lifespan during which they live inside in the blockchain and help to secure it by minting blocks. Beekeepers will earn rewards whenever one of their bees mints a block.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The key advantages of our proposal are:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Existing SHA256 miners and pools are not affected. &lt;/span&gt;Proof-of-work blocks will be accepted by the network at any time, so SHA256 mining hardware never needs to stand idle.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;51% network attacks are rendered ineffective.&lt;/span&gt; Worker bees won't mint blocks on an attacker's private chain, so they cannot accumulate enough chain work to perform a 51% hashpower attack&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;The mining process will be democratised&lt;/span&gt;, as any LCC holder can become a beekeeper.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the next major update of Litecoin Cash, this tab will allow you to easily become a beekeeper yourself. It will also be where you can keep an eye on your hive to monitor the health of your bees and see the rewards your bees have earned.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://hive.litecoinca.sh/whitepaper.pdf&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:10pt; text-decoration: underline; color:#0000ff;&quot;&gt;Learn more: Read our whitepaper on The Hive&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
